  Former
Mpumalanga premier, Matthew Phosa's eldest daughter Moyahabo Phosa (39) has
passed away after a short illness. Moya as she
is affectionately known has been in ICU for a while, and recently suffered a
stroke. She passed
away this morning in Nelspruit Mediclinic. Friends and
family were informed of her passing in a message. “It is with
deep sadness that we inform you of the passing of Moyahabo Phosa, the eldest
daughter of Mathews and Pinky. “Our
heartfelt condolences go out to the Phosa family. May her beautiful soul rest
in eternal peace."